    {
      "id": "57b33425-7ac1-475f-8a8f-770f778c7d59",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Student attrition is a significant issue in higher education and analysis of behavioral data in the LMS may be helpful for that. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "57b33425-7ac1-475f-8a8f-770f778c7d59",
        "parent": {
