    {
      "id": "649fb69d-ebb0-4843-858d-dd5cf9724403",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The paper uses a publicly available dataset to identify student attrition with ML. Findings show that it is possible to use ML to identify students at risk with 85% accuracy (RF). ",
